'''El Viñedo''' is a neighborhood in northern [[Valencia, Venezuela|Valencia]], [[Venezuela]]. It is home to many of the city's best restaurants and nightclubs; this area is known as "''La calle de los cafés''" (Café Street). El Viñedo is home to many of Valencia's best hotels: the new [[Embassy Suites Hotels|Embassy Suites]] hotel is in El Viñedo and is widely regarded as one of Valencia's best; additionally the Ucaima Hotel is located in El Viñedo. Valencia's Avenida Bolivar borders El Viñedo and once the situation with the city's metro{{explain|reason=what situation?|date=October 2015}} is solved the area will become easier to access from other zones of Valencia.

