{{Infobox artwork | image_file = Drummer flanagan.JPG | painting_alignment = Oblique Right | image_size = 300px | title = The Drummer | alt = | other_language_1 = | other_title_1 = | other_language_2 = | other_title_2 = | artist = Barry Flanagan | year = 1989-90 | type = [[Bronze]] | height_metric = | width_metric = | length_metric = | height_imperial = 96 | width_imperial = 68 | length_imperial = 36 | metric_unit = cm | imperial_unit = in | city = [[Washington, D.C.]], [[United States]] | museum = | coordinates = {{coord| 38.8889|-77.02265}} | owner = [[Smithsonian Institution]] }}
'''''The Drummer''''' is a bronze sculpture, by [[Barry Flanagan]].<ref>[http://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?&profile=all&source=~!siartinventories&uri=full=3100001~!373197~!0#focus "The Drummer, (sculpture)"]. ''SIRIS''</ref>
It is at the [[Hirshhorn Museum and Sculpture Garden]].<ref>http://hirshhorn.si.edu/visit/collection_object.asp?key=32&subkey=2823</ref>
