{{Infobox television | show_name = The Player | image = | image_alt = | genre = [[Drama (film and television)|Drama]] | writer = Djamel Fazaz | starring = {{Plainlist| * [[Mohammed Adjaimi]] * [[Fatiha Berber]] * [[Farida Krim]] * [[Samir Abdoun]] * [[Asma Djermoune]] }} | theme_music_composer = | opentheme = | endtheme = | composer = | country = Algeria | language = [[Algerian Arabic]] | num_seasons = 1 | num_episodes = 30 | list_episodes = | executive_producer = | producer = Télévision Algérienne | runtime = 35 min | company = Star Production | distributor = | network = Télévision Algérienne | picture_format = | audio_format = | first_aired = {{Start date|df=yes|2004|10|15}} | last_aired = {{Start date|df=yes|2004|11|14}} | website = | production_website = }} '''''The Player''''' ({{lang-ar|اللاعب}}, '''Al-laib''') is an [[Algeria]]n television series, produced and broadcast by [[Télévision Algérienne]], directed and written by Djamel Fazaz. It premiere on October, 2004 on [[Télévision Algérienne]], [[A3 (TV channel)|A3]] and [[Canal Algérie]].<ref name="chouf-chouf">[http://www.elcinema.com/work/1317335/ مسلسل الاعب] Retrieved Juin 24, 2017.</ref>.
It stars Mohammed Adjaimi, Fatiha Berber, Samir Abdoun and Asma Djermoune in the main role. == Cast == * [[Mohammed Adjaimi]] as Si Authmane * [[Fatiha Berber]] * [[Nawal Zaatar]] * [[Farida Krim]] * Nassima * [[Samir Abdoun]] as Reda * [[Asma Djermoune]] as Sabrina * Abd Al-krim Briber * Nawal Zmit * [[Malika Belbey]] * Lamia Bouskin * [[Sid Ali Kouiret]] * [[Bahia Rachedi]]
